OL,3,CWhat is the Lampard mental health
OL,4,CInquiry?
OL,6,FIt began as the relentless fight of
OL,7,Ftwo mothers whose sons were able to
OL,8,Ftake their own lives on a mental
OL,9,Fhealth ward in Essex.
OL,11,FMatthew Leahy's mother, Melanie, and
OL,12,FBen Morris's mother, Lisa, wanted to
OL,13,Fknow why, when their children were
OL,14,Fsupposed to be in a place of safety,
OL,15,Fthey were able to die.
OL,17,FMore than a decade later, a public
OL,18,Finquiry - the first of its kind into
OL,19,Fmental health - is underway,
OL,20,Finvestigating "in excess" of 2,000
OL,21,Fpatient deaths, over the last 20 years.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/21
