OL,3,CWhat is the Lampard mental health
OL,4,CInquiry?
OL,6,FWhat is The Lampard Inquiry?
OL,8,FNamed after its Chair, Baroness Kate
OL,9,FLampard CBE, The Lampard Inquiry is a
OL,10,Fstatutory inquiry, investigating the
OL,11,Fdeaths of inpatients who died whilst
OL,12,Fthey were living on adult and children
OL,13,Fmental health units run by the NHS in
OL,14,FEssex, between the years 2000 and the
OL,15,Fend of 2023.
OL,17,FIt will also look at deaths that
OL,18,Fhappened within three months of
OL,19,Fpatients being discharged from those
OL,20,Funits.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/21
