OL,3,CWhat is the Lampard mental health
OL,4,CInquiry?
OL,6,FPatients will also be included, if
OL,7,Fthey were assessed and refused a bed
OL,8,Fon a mental health ward, or if they
OL,9,Fwere waiting for assessment.
OL,11,FThe majority of NHS mental health
OL,12,Fservices in Essex are provided by the
OL,13,FEssex Partnership University NHS
OL,14,FFoundation Trust, which runs 35 adult
OL,15,Finpatient wards and three for children
OL,16,Fand teenagers across the county.
OL,18,FBut the inquiry will also look at
OL,19,Fdeaths that occurred while patients
OL,20,Fwere receiving NHS care in the private
OL,21,Fsector.
