OL,3,CWhat is the Lampard mental health
OL,4,CInquiry?
OL,6,FThe inquiry opened on September 9,
OL,7,Fwith Baroness Lampard saying the
OL,8,Fnumber of deaths being looked into
OL,9,Fwill likely be "significantly in
OL,10,Fexcess" of 2,000.
OL,12,FWhat does it hope to achieve?
OL,14,FThe Lampard Inquiry has put services
OL,15,Facross Essex firmly in the spotlight.
