OL,6,FBut the repeated failures in Essex
OL,7,Fover the last two decades could be
OL,8,Findicative of what is going on
OL,9,Felsewhere in the UK, and this inquiry
OL,10,Fcould have ramifications for all NHS
OL,11,Fmental health provision.
OL,13,FBaroness Lampard has made it clear she
OL,14,Fwants the findings of this inquiry to
OL,15,Fhelp improve mental healthcare across
OL,16,Fthe country, saying "we can make
OL,17,Frecommendations for real and lasting
OL,18,Fchange in memory of those who have
OL,19,Flost their lives as mental health
OL,20,Fpatients in Essex".
