OL,6,FWhat powers does the Lampard Inquiry
OL,7,Fhave?
OL,9,FThe Lampard Inquiry, which is funded
OL,10,Fand backed by the government, is
OL,11,Findependent, as is the chair, Baroness
OL,12,FLampard.
OL,14,FShe is a former barrister, who in 2015
OL,15,Fled a report into the relationship
OL,16,Fbetween former broadcaster Jimmy
OL,17,FSavile and NHS hospitals.
OL,19,FBaroness Lampard is also a member of
OL,20,Fthe House of Lords, but is not
OL,21,Faffiliated to a political party.
