OL,3,CWhat is the Lampard mental health
OL,4,CInquiry?
OL,6,FThe Lampard Inquiry has statutory
OL,7,Fstatus, which means it can legally
OL,8,Fforce witnesses to give evidence.
OL,10,FIt is an important difference for some
OL,11,Ffamilies and campaigners, who were
OL,12,Funhappy with the original, non-
OL,13,Fstatutory inquiry, the Essex Mental
OL,14,FHealth Independent Inquiry - which
OL,15,Fstarted in 2021, but had to be
OL,16,Fabandoned after only 11 members of
OL,17,Fstaff, out of the 14,000 that were
OL,18,Fcontacted, agreed to give evidence.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/21
