OL,3,CWhat is the Lampard mental health
OL,4,CInquiry?
OL,6,FIn 2008, 20-year-old Ben Morris called
OL,7,Fhis mum, Lisa, and said he wanted to
OL,8,Fleave the Linden Centre in Chelmsford.
OL,10,FThirty minutes later he was found
OL,11,Fdead. He had a diagnosis of attention
OL,12,Fdeficit hyperactivity disorder (ADHD)
OL,13,Fand an inquest concluded he died by
OL,14,Fsuicide.
OL,16,FIn 2012, days after reporting being
OL,17,Fraped on the unit, and only a week
OL,18,Fafter he was admitted to the Linden
OL,19,FCentre, 20-year-old Matthew Leahy was
OL,20,Ffound unresponsive in his room.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/21
