OL,7,Fsectioned and detained under the
OL,8,FMental Health Act, and was suffering
OL,9,Fwith psychosis.
OL,11,FIn 2017, police said records of
OL,12,FMatthew's care plan had been
OL,13,Ffalsified, but no action was taken.
