OL,3,CWhat is the Lampard mental health
OL,4,CInquiry?
OL,6,FMelanie began petitioning for a public
OL,7,Finquiry into the death of her son, and
OL,8,Fher campaign gained momentum, with
OL,9,Fmany other bereaved families joining
OL,10,Fher.
OL,12,FBy 2020 she had raised the more than
OL,13,F100,000 signatures needed to force a
OL,14,Fdebate in Parliament.
OL,16,FIn November, that debate, on the state
OL,17,Fof mental healthcare in Essex took
OL,18,Fplace, where an independent inquiry
OL,19,Finto deaths at the Linden Centre was
OL,20,Fannounced by the then MP and Health
OL,21,FMinister Nadine Dorries.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G13/21
