OL,3,CWhat is the Lampard mental health
OL,4,CInquiry?
OL,6,FA few months later, in 2021, the Essex
OL,7,FMental Health Independent Inquiry was
OL,8,Festablished, with Dr Geraldine
OL,9,FStrathdee as its chair.
OL,11,FThen, in June, EPUT pleaded guilty to
OL,12,Ffailing to prevent patient suicides,
OL,13,Ffollowing an investigation by the
OL,14,FHealth and Safety Executive into the
OL,15,Fdeaths of 11 inpatients between 2004
OL,16,Fand 2015.
OL,18,FBen Morris and Matthew Leahy were
OL,19,Fincluded in that 11.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G14/21
