OL,3,CWhat is the Lampard mental health
OL,4,CInquiry?
OL,6,FThe Trust accepted that its
OL,7,Fpredecessor, the North Essex Trust,
OL,8,Fhad failed to properly manage fixed
OL,9,Fligature points in its units, at seven
OL,10,Fof its sites, and it was fined #1.5
OL,11,Fmillion. The judge said there had been
OL,12,Fa "litany of failures".
OL,14,FBy 2022, the inquiry announced it was
OL,15,Flooking into some 1,500 unexpected,
OL,16,Funexplained and self-inflicted deaths
OL,17,Fof Essex Partnership University Trust
OL,18,Fpatients between 2000 and 2020.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G15/21
