OL,6,FThis number was later updated to
OL,7,F2,000. But, despite repeated calls for
OL,8,Fstaff members to come forward and give
OL,9,Fevidence, by 2023, the inquiry was
OL,10,Fabandoned, with the chair writing to
OL,11,Fthe then health secretary Steve
OL,12,FBarclay MP to say she will not be able
OL,13,Fto complete the work if the inquiry
OL,14,Fwas not given legal powers to force
OL,15,Fwitnesses.
OL,17,FIn June, it was converted to a
OL,18,Fstatutory inquiry and Dr Strathdee
OL,19,Fstood down for personal reasons.
OL,20,FBaroness Lampard was then appointed as
OL,21,Fthe new chair.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G16/21
