OL,6,FWhat concerns will the Lampard Inquiry
OL,7,Fexamine?
OL,9,FWhat has the NHS said?
OL,11,FIn its opening statement to the
OL,12,Finquiry, Essex Partnership University
OL,13,FNHS Foundation Trust apologised to
OL,14,Fpatients and families for "failing"
OL,15,Fthem.
OL,17,FSpeaking on behalf of the Trust,
OL,18,FEleanor Grey KC acknowledged a series
OL,19,Fof failings, including allegations of
OL,20,Fsexual assault by staff.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G17/21
