OL,4,CInquiry?
OL,6,FMs Grey also outlined a number of
OL,7,Fsteps already taken to improve safety
OL,8,Fon the wards, including 1,700 new
OL,9,Fstaff, introducing new technology -
OL,10,Flike body worn cameras - and more than
OL,11,F#6 million spent on removing fixed
OL,12,Fligature risks.
OL,14,FBut she went on to question the number
OL,15,Fof deaths being looked into by the
OL,16,Finquiry, saying the investigation
OL,17,Fwould include patients who died of
OL,18,Fnatural causes, such as a heart
OL,19,Fattack, while living on mental health
OL,20,Fwards.
